SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

FROM "Courses" AS "c"

        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"

    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"

) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"

FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"

SELECT "c"."Id", "c"."Description", "c"."Title", "t1"."Id", "t1"."CourseId", "t1"."Description", "t1"."Title", "t1"."Id0", "t1"."Description0", "t1"."Title0", "t1"."TopicId", "t1"."Id00", "t1"."Content", "t1"."SubTopicId", "t1"."Title00"
FROM "Courses" AS "c"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."CourseId", "t"."Description", "t"."Title", "t0"."Id" AS "Id0", "t0"."Description" AS "Description0", "t0"."Title" AS "Title0", "t0"."TopicId", "t0"."Id0" AS "Id00", "t0"."Content", "t0"."SubTopicId", "t0"."Title0" AS "Title00"
    FROM "Topics" AS "t"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."Description", "s"."Title", "s"."TopicId", "l"."Id" AS "Id0", "l"."Content", "l"."SubTopicId", "l"."Title" AS "Title0"
        FROM "SubTopics" AS "s"
        LEFT JOIN "Lessons" AS "l" ON "s"."Id" = "l"."SubTopicId"
    ) AS "t0" ON "t"."Id" = "t0"."TopicId"
) AS "t1" ON "c"."Id" = "t1"."CourseId"
ORDER BY "c"."Id", "t1"."Id", "t1"."Id0"
